are no longer the Engineer. You are the #strong[Client];. \*
#strong[Your Input:] "Create a system to move 50kg loads in a rainy
warehouse." \* #strong[MSS Action:] It triggers the PUDAL Design Cycle.
\* #strong[Result:] It outputs a blueprint, a software stack, and a
procurement list for the Target System.
